		<div>I agree with Quichon and Dunthor - I want the super trophy to be useful for tradeskills primarily. I don't care about hps/mana/saves/etc on my trophies. I use them for Primary Stat (to boost my total for skillups), Cha (to buy cheaper/sell higher) and Str (to carry more). Something on the order of +25 to Wis/Int/Str and +100 Cha (to help those tradeskillers penalized with a very low starting Cha). I can see an argument for adding Dex as well.<br />
