<br />
I am NOT 1750 yet, but I am making my trophies as I go along. Why? Because I want to...I like to know that I've finished a tradeskill and for me, the trophy is the expression of that goal. I want the super trophy to reflect the same ideals as why I enjoy tradeskills in the first place, not to be some uber piece of equipment that high end players will covet. Aid Grimmel sounds like a fun quest... but for those of us not in high end quilds, it's more a fantasy than reality.<br />
